(258, 'OBJ', 'GBK', 'Yr1', 'BLS', 5, '<p>According to Peter, what &ldquo;covers a multitude of sins&rdquo;?</p>'),
(259, 'OBJ', 'GBK', 'Yr1', 'BLS', 5, '<p>In prison, for whom did Joseph interpret dreams?</p>'),
(260, 'OBJ', 'GBK', 'Yr1', 'BLS', 5, '<p>To what preservative does the Lord compare his disciples?</p>'),
