(6, 'OBJ', 'JAMB', 'YrK14', 'ECO', 4, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></em><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" style=\"height:36px; width:178px\" /></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>= N18m</p>'),
(6, 'OBJ', 'JAMB', 'YrK18', 'MTH', 4, '<div><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" style=\"height:32px; width:142px\" /></span></span></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">5x - 6y = 7 ----------equation(i) x 2</span></span></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">2x - 7y = -11 -------equation(ii) x 5</span></span></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">10x - 12y = 14</span></span></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><u>-(10x - 35y = -55</u>)</span></span></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;23y = 69</span></span></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">divide both sides by 23</span></span></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">y = 3</span></span></span></span></div>'),
(6, 'OBJ', 'NCEE', 'YrK06', 'MTH', 2, '<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Let x and y be the numbers</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">If x = -3</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">then -3y = 24</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Divide both sides by -3</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">y = <sup>24</sup>/<sub>-3</sub></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">y = -8</span></div>'),
(6, 'OBJ', 'NCEE', 'YrK07', 'MTH', 2, '<div>Rearrange the numbers is Ascending or Descending order = 1, 6, <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">7</span>, 8, 8</div>\r\n<div>Since the sum of the elements is odd i.e 5 elements in all, the middle element is the 3rd element, and that is 7</div>'),
