(8, 'OBJ', 'NCEE', 'YrK19', 'QTR', 2, '<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">2<sup>2</sup> - 2<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">= 4 - 4</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">= 0</span></div>'),
(8, 'OBJ', 'WASSCE', 'YrK18', 'ENG', 1, '<p>The word departure means;&nbsp;an&nbsp;act&nbsp;or&nbsp;instance&nbsp;of&nbsp;departing: Depart means;&nbsp;to go&nbsp;away;&nbsp;leave:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>While</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Arrival which means; an&nbsp;act&nbsp;of arriving;&nbsp;a&nbsp;coming, is the most suitable answer.</p>'),
