(9, 'OBJ', 'NCEE', 'YrK19', 'MTH', 2, '<div><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Girls : Boys = 30 : 45</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Divide both values by H.C.F of 15</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Girls : Boys = 2:3</span></div>'),
(9, 'OBJ', 'NCEE', 'YrK19', 'QTR', 2, '<div>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria Math&quot;,serif\">&nbsp;</span></em><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" style=\"height:59px; width:63px\" /></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</div>'),
(9, 'OBJ', 'WASSCE', 'YrK18', 'ENG', 1, '<p>The word complicated means&nbsp;difficult&nbsp;to&nbsp;analyze,&nbsp;understand,&nbsp;explain,&nbsp;etc.:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>While simple means;&nbsp;easy&nbsp;to&nbsp;understand,&nbsp;deal&nbsp;with,&nbsp;use,&nbsp;</p>'),
(10, 'OBJ', 'GBK', 'Yr1', 'BLS', 5, '<p>Ruth 1:4</p>\r\n<p>And they took them wives of the women of Moab; the name of the one was Orpah, and the name of the other Ruth: and they dwelled there about ten years</p>'),
(10, 'OBJ', 'JAMB', 'YrK16', 'ECO', 4, '<p>Income = Investment&nbsp;&divide; MPS</p>\r\n<p>MPS = 1 - MPC</p>\r\n<p>MPS = 1 -&nbsp;<sup>2</sup>/<sub>3</sub> =&nbsp;<sup>1</sup>/<sub>3</sub></p>\r\n<p>Income = N100million &divide;&nbsp;<sup>1</sup>/<sub>3</sub></p>\r\n<p>Income = N300million</p>'),
(10, 'OBJ', 'NCEE', 'YrK06', 'MTH', 2, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" style=\"height:121px; width:155px\" /></span></span></span></span></p>'),
(10, 'OBJ', 'NCEE', 'YrK07', 'MTH', 2, '<div>Area of Big rectangle = length x Breadth</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= 10cm x 9cm = 90cm<sup>2</sup></div>\r\n\r\n<div>Area of Small rectangle = length x Breadth</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= 8cm x 7cm = 56cm<sup>2</sup></div>\r\n\r\n<div>Area of shaded region = area of big rectangle - area of small rectangle</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;= 90cm<sup>2</sup> - 56cm<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;=&nbsp;34cm<sup>2</sup></div>'),
(10, 'OBJ', 'NCEE', 'YrK09', 'MTH', 2, '<div><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Let the number be x</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" style=\"height:52px; width:80px\" /></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>when we cross multiply</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">2x = 30</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>when you divide both sides by 2</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">x = 15</span></p>\r\n</div>'),
