(10, 'OBJ', 'WASSCE', 'YrK18', 'ENG', 1, '<p>The word unassuming means;&nbsp;modest;&nbsp;unpretentious, while boastful means;&nbsp;given&nbsp;to or&nbsp;characterized&nbsp;by boasting.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Boasting means;&nbsp;to&nbsp;speak&nbsp;with&nbsp;exaggeration&nbsp;and&nbsp;excessive&nbsp;pride,&nbsp;especially&nbsp;about&nbsp;oneself.</p>'),
(11, 'OBJ', 'GBK', 'Yr1', 'BLS', 5, '<p>Judges 16:30</p>'),
(11, 'OBJ', 'JAMB', 'YrK17', 'ECO', 4, '<p>Average Cost = Total Cost&nbsp;&divide; Output</p>\r\n<p>Total Cost = total fixed cost + total variable cost</p>\r\n<p>Average cost = (N1000 + N2500)&nbsp;&divide; 100</p>\r\n<p>Average Cost = N3500&nbsp;&divide; 100</p>\r\n<p>Average Cost = N35</p>'),
(11, 'OBJ', 'NCEE', 'YrK06', 'MTH', 2, '<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">If z+2 =8</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">then z = 8 - 2</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">z = 6</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">therefore z<sup>2</sup> + 5</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">= (6 x 6) + 5</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">= 36 + 5</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">= 41</span></div>'),
(11, 'OBJ', 'NCEE', 'YrK07', 'MTH', 2, '<div>If seven days make 1 week</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">128 days</span>&nbsp; = 18 weeks remainder 2 days</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;7 days</div>'),
(11, 'OBJ', 'NCEE', 'YrK09', 'MTH', 2, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" style=\"height:122px; width:204px\" /></span></span></span></span></p>'),
(11, 'OBJ', 'NCEE', 'YrK11', 'QTR', 2, '<div>? = 5 + (3 x 3)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;= 5 + 9</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;= 14</div>'),
(11, 'OBJ', 'NCEE', 'YrK12', 'QTR', 2, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" style=\"height:34px; width:42px\" /></span></span></span></span></p>'),
(11, 'OBJ', 'NCEE', 'YrK13', 'QTR', 2, '<div>? = (3 x 6) + (5 - 2)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>= 18 + 3</div>\r\n\r\n<div>= 21</div>'),
(11, 'OBJ', 'NCEE', 'YrK14', 'MTH', 2, '<div><strong>Step 1:&nbsp;</strong>Find the l.c.m of the denominators which is 60</div>\r\n\r\n<div><strong>Step 2:&nbsp;</strong>Convert the fractions with common denominator</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;<sup>2</sup>/<sub>5</sub> = <sup>24</sup>/<sub>60</sub></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;<sup>1</sup>/<sub>2</sub> = <sup>30</sup>/<sub>60</sub></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;<sup>1</sup>/<sub>3</sub> = <sup>20</sup>/<sub>60</sub></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;<sup>3</sup>/<sub>4</sub> = <sup>45</sup>/<sub>60</sub></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;<sup>2</sup>/<sub>3</sub> = <sup>40</sup>/<sub>60</sub></div>\r\n\r\n<div><sub>the smallest of them all is&nbsp;</sub><sup>1</sup>/<sub>3</sub> = <sup>20</sup>/<sub>60</sub></div>');
