(11, 'OBJ', 'WASSCE', 'YrK18', 'ENG', 1, '<p>Bonus:&nbsp;a&nbsp;sum&nbsp;of&nbsp;money&nbsp;granted&nbsp;or&nbsp;given&nbsp;to an&nbsp;employee, in&nbsp;addition&nbsp;to&nbsp;regular&nbsp;pay,usually&nbsp;in&nbsp;appreciation&nbsp;for&nbsp;work&nbsp;done,&nbsp;length&nbsp;of&nbsp;service,&nbsp;accumulated&nbsp;favors,&nbsp;etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Plural&nbsp;<strong>bonuses</strong></p>'),
(12, 'OBJ', 'GBK', 'Yr1', 'BLS', 5, '<p>Genesis 4:9</p>\r\n<p>And the&nbsp;<span class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>&nbsp;said unto <strong>Cain</strong>, Where is Abel thy brother? And he said, I know not: Am I my brother\'s keeper?</p>'),
(12, 'OBJ', 'NCEE', 'YrK06', 'MTH', 2, '<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">6x + 3x - x = 24</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">8x = 24</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Divide both sides by 8</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">x = <sup>24</sup>/<sub>8</sub></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\">x = 3</span></div>'),
(12, 'OBJ', 'NCEE', 'YrK07', 'MTH', 2, '<div>Total = Ani + Obi + Fawusa</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; =&nbsp;2<sup>1</sup>/<sub>2</sub>m + 4<sup>1</sup>/<sub>2</sub>m + 3<sup>1</sup>/<sub>2</sub>m</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; =(2 + 4 + 3) + (<sup>1</sup>/<sub>2&nbsp;</sub>+<sup>1</sup>/<sub>2</sub>&nbsp;+&nbsp;<sup>1</sup>/<sub>2</sub>)m</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = 9 +&nbsp;<sup>3</sup>/<sub>2</sub>m</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = 9 + 1<sup>1</sup>/<sub>2</sub>m</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = 10<sup>1</sup>/<sub>2</sub>m</div>'),
